contentCards.title: Durable Polycotton Fabric
contentCards.description: Crafted from a high-quality polycotton blend, this shirt ensures long-lasting durability and comfort. The fabric is breathable and easy to maintain, making it ideal for everyday wear. Stay comfortable and stylish all day long.

contentCards.title: Casual and Trendy
contentCards.description: Whether you're heading out for a casual outing or a weekend brunch, this shirt is perfect for any casual occasion. Its versatile design and trendy solid pattern make it a must-have in your wardrobe.

contentCards.title: Classic Button Down Collar
contentCards.description: Designed with a classic button-down collar, this shirt exudes a timeless charm. The collar adds a touch of sophistication to your overall look and can be easily dressed up or down for different occasions.

headers.name: Chest
headers.guideline: Measure around the body under the arms at the fullest part of the chest with your arms relaxed at both sides.

headers.name: Shoulder
headers.guideline: Measure the shoulder at the back, from edge to edge with arms relaxed on both sides

headers.name: Length
headers.guideline: Measure from the highest point of the shoulder seam to the bottom hem of the garment's

headers.name: Sleeve Length
headers.guideline: Measure from the shoulder seam through the outer arm to the cuff/hem

guideline.title: Full Sleeve Shirts
guideline.text:
Not sure about your shirt size? Follow these simple steps to figure it out: 
***Shoulder*** - Measure the shoulder at the back, from edge to edge with arms relaxed on both sides 
***Chest*** - Measure around the body under the arms at the fullest part of the chest with your arms relaxed at both sides. 
***Sleeve*** - Measure from the shoulder seam through the outer arm to the cuff/hem 
***Neck*** - Measured horizontally across the neck 
***Length*** - Measure from the highest point of the shoulder seam to the bottom hem of the garment's

guideline.title: Half Sleeve Shirts
guideline.text:
